178
00:11:25.859 --> 00:11:27.295
- (loud thud)
- Hey. yo!

179
00:11:27.512 --> 00:11:29.732
Who left one spoon
of chocolate in the can?

180
00:11:31.647 --> 00:11:33.040
(man) Dang...

181
00:11:34.302 --> 00:11:36.217
